# Large binary assets
*.png
*.png.meta
*.zip
*.zip.meta

# Logo assets that ship with the package (release zip needs these)
!Editor/Settings/Logos/*.png
!Editor/Settings/Logos/*.png.meta

# Public site assets (GitHub Pages serves docs/)
!docs/assets/*.png
docs/**/*.meta
docs.meta

# Bridge binaries: built locally via Editor/Bridge~/UnityAgentBridge/build.{ps1,sh}
# or in CI at release time.
#
# Binary-level .meta files are also ignored — Unity auto-generates them next to
# the binary when present, and CI writes canonical ones (with fixed GUIDs) into
# the release zip. Folder-level .meta files under Editor/Bridge/bin/ ARE tracked
# so folder GUIDs stay stable across installs.
Editor/Bridge/bin/*/UnityAgentBridge
Editor/Bridge/bin/*/UnityAgentBridge.exe
Editor/Bridge/bin/*/UnityAgentBridge.meta
Editor/Bridge/bin/*/UnityAgentBridge.exe.meta

# brainstorming sessions (visual companion)
.superpowers/

# internal design docs (specs/plans — not part of the published package)
docs/superpowers/
